{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-312-cyclic-paths-on-sierpiski-graphs","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 312: Ciklusi na Sierpinski grafovima","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<ul>\n<li>Graf Sierpiński stepena 1 ($S_1$) je jednakostranični trougao.</li>\n<li>$S_{n + 1}$ se dobija iz $S_n$ postavljanjem tri kopije $S_n$ na način da par kopija ima jedan zajednički vrh.</li>\n</ul>\n<img alt=\"Sierpinski graphs of order-1 to order-5\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/cyclic-paths-on-sierpinski-graphs-1.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Neka $C(n)$ bude broj ciklusa koji prolazi samo jednom kroz svaki vrh od $S_n$. Na primer, $C(3) = 8$ zato što osam takvih ciklusa može se nacrtati na $S_3$, kao što je prikazano ispod:</p>\n<img alt=\"eight cycles that pass exactly once through all vertices of S_3\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/cyclic-paths-on-sierpinski-graphs-2.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Takođe se može potvrditi da:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; C(1) = C(2) = 1 \\\\\n&#x26; C(5) = 71,328,803,586,048 \\\\\n&#x26; C(10 000)\\bmod {10}^8 = 37,652,224 \\\\\n&#x26; C(10 000)\\bmod {13}^8 = 617,720,485 \\\\\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Pronađi $C(C(C(10\\,000)))\\bmod {13}^8$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4a51000cf542c50ffb7","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301968,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-312-cyclic-paths-on-sierpiski-graphs"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function pathsOnSierpinskiGraphs() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\npathsOnSierpinskiGraphs();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>pathsOnSierpinskiGraphs()</code> treba da return <code>324681947</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(pathsOnSierpinskiGraphs(), 324681947);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-312-cyclic-paths-on-sierpiski-graphs","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-313-sliding-game","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-311-biclinic-integral-quadrilaterals","id":"5900f4a51000cf542c50ffb7","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-312-cyclic-paths-on-sierpiski-graphs"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}